These numbers are meaningless. Really. They excite me the same as when i got my first thousand plays. Your experience in music is relative. To my artist friends and hopefuls, dont chase numbers. Chase that little feeling in your stomach when you’re nervous about a release. Chase that excitement when you see your music impacting people. Chase the crushing disappointment of emotional learning when your song fizzles out. you’ll be ok. just keep chasing. Thank you for another year of getting to do this. #music #spotifywrapped

Love my fans. Thank you to the folks at @cyberpunkgame @easportsufc @thesims @boredapeyachtclub @leagueoflegends and so many more for giving me a platform to share my music with the world!! (song in bg playing is unreleased by me and my lil bro @37_heartbreak )
Cant verbalize the love I got for these two gents. Absolute gems.
